(10, 'Guess', 'Guess Viktor Derby Brown Formal Shoes', '"Brown"', 105, 'M', 'Formal', 'Derby', 'Make an impression when wearing these brown coloured formal shoes by Guess. Offering optimum traction on a wet or dry floor, its TPR (thermoplastic rubber) soles will complement the sleek design of this pair of formal shoes. Featuring synthetic upper and lining, these trendy formal sh', 'Color: Brown\r\nUpper Material: Synthetic Leather\r\nSole Material: TPR\r\nClosing: Lace-up\r\nTip shape: Round\r\nAnkle Height: Low Ankle\r\nShoe Weight: Regular (373 GM)\r\nProduct warranty3 Month Against Manufacturing Defects\r\nShoe Care: Surface Dirt can be cleaned with a good quality brush or a damp cloth.\r\nSKU: KN667SH80TTBINDFAS', 'GuessViktorDerbyBrownFormalShoes.jpg', 'F', 'F'),
(12, 'Salvatore Ferragamo', 'Salvatore Ferragamo Guillame Loafers', '"Cuoio Leather", "Nero Leather", "Rosso Leather"', 374, 'M', 'Formal', 'Loafers', 'A satin-finish Gancio bit tops a handsome Italian driving shoe fashioned from smooth leather.', '    Slip-on style.\r\n    Rubber driver sole.\r\n    Leather upper and lining/rubber sole.\r\n    By Salvatore Ferragamo made in Italy.\r\n    Men''s Shoes.', 'SalvatoreFerragamoGuillameLoafers.jpg', 'F', 'F'),
