(54, 'Birkenstock', ' Milano Habana Oiled Leather Womens', '"Brown"', 125, 'F', 'Casual', 'Sandals', 'The Milano is similar to our iconic Arizona but the added heel strap helps it stay on your foot a bit better. All three straps have an adjustable buckle for a great fit. Offered in classic footbed in Habana Oiled Leather. Made in Germany. ', 'Upper material: Oiled Leather - thick yet supple leather is breathable, durable and comfortable. Softens with wear.\r\nFootbed: The classic Birkenstock footbed - features pronounced arch support, a deep heel cup, and a roomy toe box. The footbed conforms to the shape of your foot.\r\n    Sole material: EVA - flexible, lightweight, durable and shock absorbing.\r\n', 'MilanoHabanaOiledLeather.jpg', 'F', 'F'),
(55, 'Birkenstock', ' Gizeh Habana Oiled Leather Womens', '"Brown"', 152, 'F', 'Casual', 'Sandals', 'The Gizeh is our most iconic thong sandal with a stylish but clean look that''s perfect for almost any outfit. The toe piece is made of flexible resin, anatomically designed to fit comfortably between the toes and the strap has a buckle for a secure fit. Offered in classic footbed in Habana Oiled Leather. ', 'Upper material: Oiled Leather - thick yet supple leather is breathable, durable and comfortable. Softens with wear.\r\nFootbed: The classic Birkenstock footbed - features pronounced arch support, a deep heel cup, and a roomy toe box. The footbed conforms to the shape of your foot.\r\nSole material: EVA - flexible, lightweight, durable and shock absorbing.\r\n', 'GizehHabanaOiledLeather.jpg', 'F', 'F'),
(56, 'Birkenstock', ' Arizona Soft Footbed Brown Amalfi Leather Womens', '"Brown"', 135, 'F', 'Casual', 'Sandals', 'Our iconic two-strap style, the Arizona, is known for being the epitome of comfort. Both straps have buckles for a fantastic fit. Offered in soft footbed in Brown Amalfi Leather. Made in Germany. ', 'Upper material: Amalfi Leather - thick yet supple leather that is breathable, durable and comfortable.\r\nFootbed: Soft footbed - a foam layer is inserted between the cork layer and the suede liner of the classic Birkenstock footbed. This layer features an extremely high degree of rebound capacity which permits long-lasting cushioning.\r\nSole material: EVA - flexible, lightweight, durable and shock absorbing.\r\n', 'ArizonaSoftFootbedBrownAmalfiLeather.jpg', 'F', 'F'),
