(58, 'New Balance', 'New Balance 996 Distinct Mid-Century Womens', '"Desert Brown"', 155, 'F', 'Casual', 'Sneakers', 'The New Balance 996 has always been a staple in NBâ€™s retro running category, and today a classic combination of suede and mesh hits in one of the cleanest offerings in recent memory. A durable white suede serves as the base throughout while breathable mesh hits on the toe, tongue, and ankle collar. Accents of dark grey and obsidian hit the branding and ENCAPÂ® midsole. Are you a fan of the look? Continue onward for a better look at the latest NB 996 below and pick up this pair from select shops like Sole Mate today for $155', '- Faux suede, textile upper upper\r\n- Round toe\r\n- Lace up fastening\r\n- 7 pairs of eyelets\r\n- Flat lace\r\n- Textile insole', 'NewBalance996DistinctMid-CenturyModernWomens.jpg', 'F', 'T'),
