(60, 'KEEN', 'KEEN Womens City of Palms', '"Brown"', 95, 'F', 'Casual', 'Palms', 'Fit Tip: Most customers find this style is true to size!\r\nMeasurement Note: Our measurements were taken using a Womenâ€™s size 7 US (37.5 EU). Measurements may vary by size.', 'Approximate weight per shoe: 5.8 oz/ 164 g\r\nStyle: Sandals\r\nCollections: Casual\r\nCategory: Casual\r\nActivity: City, Beach\r\nWeather: Warm\r\nGender: Women\r\nUpper: Leather', 'KEENWomensCityofPalms.jpg', 'F', 'F'),
(61, 'Taylor Palm', 'Off White Womens Palms', '"White"', 36, 'F', 'Casual', 'Palms', 'Building on the popular man-tailored trend, this T-bar style is a great transitional choice. A metallic buckle fastening, surface detailing and a low heel add glamorous touches while Cushion Softâ„¢ layers provide a comfortable fit. The off white patent and dainty pointed toe finish the look. Take a look at our blog for ideas on how to style this shoe.', 'Upper Material: 	Leather\r\nLining Material:	Textile\r\nHeel Height: 1 inch\r\nSole Material: TR\r\nFastening Type: Buckle\r\nRemovable Insole: No\r\nTrims: Adjustable Strap, Buckle', 'OffWhiteWomensPalms.jpg', 'F', 'F'),
(62, 'Nike', 'Nike Free RN Motion Flyknit', '"Jade", "Blue", "Oreo"', 150, 'F', 'Sports', 'Running', 'Nike''s most natural ride to date, the Nike Free RN Motion Flyknit Women''s Running Shoe features a supportive, conforming Flyknit upper and a revolutionary new midsole pattern that allows the shoe to expand, flex and contract with your foot during every stepâ€”so you can move more freely than ever before.\r\n\r\nSuperior Natural Movement\r\n\r\nThe next-generation Nike Free midsole expands in multiple directions thanks to an entirely new tri-star pattern, adding a new dimension of flexibility that delivers maximum dynamic movement with every stride. Plus, the heel is rounded to mimic the shape of your foot and roll naturally with the ground.\r\n\r\nEnhanced Cushioning\r\n\r\nThe dual-density midsole uses a softer foam core directly underfoot and a slightly firmer foam carrier to deliver cushioned comfort and durability for a smooth, natural ride.\r\n\r\nSnug Fit\r\n\r\nStrong, single-seam Flyknit includes stretchy polyester yarn for a compressive fit that moves flawlessly with your foot as you run. Flywire cables woven into the upper can be tightened through the laces for dynamic support.', 'Notched collar for easy on and off\r\nRounded heel for natural range of motion\r\nLightweight solid rubber segments under the toe and heel for enhanced traction and durability\r\nOffset: 4mm', 'NikeFreeRNMotionFlyknit.jpg', 'F', 'F'),
(63, 'Nike', 'Nike Free Running Shoes', '"Black/Green", "Volt"', 100, 'F', 'Sports', 'Running', 'More cushioned than the Nike Free RN Motion Flyknit, the Nike Free RN Women''s Running Shoe features a newly designed midsole pattern that expands, flexes and contracts with your foot with every step. Its lightweight, breathable mesh upper helps keep your feet cool and comfortable from start to finish.\r\n\r\nMove Naturally\r\n\r\nThe next-generation Nike Free midsole expands in multiple directions thanks to an entirely new tri-star pattern, adding a new dimension of flexibility that lets your feet move more dynamically with every stride. Plus, the heel is rounded to mimic the shape of your foot and roll naturally with the ground.\r\n\r\nSoft Cushioning\r\n\r\nSofter than previous iterations, the new midsole foam delivers exceptionally comfortable cushioning and lightweight durability for miles.\r\n\r\nFlexible, Breathable Support\r\n\r\nEngineered mesh provides lightweight, flexible support and breathable comfort. Flywire cables integrate with the laces and can be adjusted for an adaptive fit.', 'Minimal sockliner molds to the shape of your foot for added support\r\nLightweight solid rubber segments under the toe and heel for enhanced traction and durability\r\nWeight: 6.9 ounces (women''s size 8)', 'NikeFreeRunningShoes.jpg', 'F', 'F'),
(64, 'Nike', 'Nike Flyknit Air Max Womens', '"White/Black", "Pink/Blue"', 225, 'F', 'Sports', 'Training', 'Ultralight support meets maximum cushioning in the Nike Flyknit Air Max Women''s Running Shoe, featuring the most flexible Max Air unit yet and a woven one-piece Flyknit upper.\r\n\r\nMaximum, Flexible Cushioning\r\n\r\nThe full-length Max Air unit offers the most flexibility to date while still delivering maximum cushioning for ultimate comfort on your run. Its tubular construction allows more air underfoot to encourage even transitions from heel strike through toe-off.\r\n\r\nUltralight Support\r\n\r\nThe ultralight Flyknit upper contours to your foot for a comfortable, supportive fit. Made entirely of polyester yarn, the single-layer construction seamlessly integrates areas of high breathability, stretch and support where you need it most.\r\n\r\nSmooth Ride\r\n\r\nThe lighter Waffle pattern outsole has been redesigned to distribute your weight more evenly for a smoother ride and enhanced traction.', 'Flywire technology integrates with the laces for a dynamic, supportive fit\r\nStitch and turn collar for a snug, comfortable fit\r\nSculpted Cushlon midsole for plush cushioning, springy resilience and impact protection\r\nFlex grooves align with the Max Air unit for more natural range of motion\r\nReflective elements enhance visibility in low light', 'NikeFlyknitAirMaxWomens.jpg', 'F', 'F'),
(65, 'Nike', 'Nike FS Lite Run 3', '"Black Pink", "Pink Blast"', 60, 'F', 'Sports', 'Training', 'The Nike FS Lite Run 3 Women''s Running Shoe is made with Breathe Tech for lightweight support. No-sew overlays, flex grooves and responsive cushioning enhance comfort and movement for your run.\r\n\r\nBenefits\r\nMidfoot Breathe Tech construction fuses foam and mesh for a lightweight support\r\nDual-density foam midsole for lightweight, responsive cushioning\r\nNo-sew overlays offer support and enhanced breathability\r\nHexagonal lugs provide multi-surface traction\r\nTargeted rubber outsole pods for enhanced durability\r\nFlex grooves promote natural range of motion', 'Weight: 7.15 ounces (women''s size 8)\r\nOffset: 3mm', 'NikeFSLiteRun3.jpg', 'T', 'F'),
(66, 'Nike', 'Nike Zoom Streak LT 3', '"Blue", "Lime Green"', 80, 'F', 'Sports', 'Training', 'The Nike Zoom Streak LT 3 Racing Shoe is built with a new last and wider forefoot to increase toe spring. This update works with the midfoot shank to add even more response off multiple surfaces.\r\n\r\nAvailable in men''s sizes. Reference the Size Chart above to convert a women''s size to men''s. ', 'Engineered mesh with an arch band locks the foot down\r\nUpdated last has more room in the forefoot to enhance toe spring\r\nFull-length Cushlon midsole with Nike Zoom unit in the heel for ultra-lightweight, responsive cushioning\r\nMidfoot shank for snappy response\r\nCrash rail and decoupled toe encourage a smooth transition\r\nBlown rubber Waffle outsole for durable, firmer cushioning and traction', 'NikeZoomStreakLT3.jpg', 'F', 'F'),
(67, 'Birkenstock', ' Arizona Soft Footbed Brown Amalfi Leather', '"Brown"', 135, 'M', 'Casual', 'Sandals', 'Our iconic two-strap style, the Arizona, is known for being the epitome of comfort. Both straps have buckles for a fantastic fit. Offered in soft footbed in Brown Amalfi Leather. Made in Germany. ', 'Upper material: Amalfi Leather - thick yet supple leather that is breathable, durable and comfortable.\r\nFootbed: Soft footbed - a foam layer is inserted between the cork layer and the suede liner of the classic Birkenstock footbed. This layer features an extremely high degree of rebound capacity which permits long-lasting cushioning.\r\nSole material: EVA - flexible, lightweight, durable and shock absorbing.\r\n', 'ArizonaSoftFootbedBrownAmalfiLeather.jpg', 'F', 'F'),
(68, 'Birkenstock', ' Milano Habana Oiled Leather', '"Brown"', 125, 'M', 'Casual', 'Sandals', 'The Milano is similar to our iconic Arizona but the added heel strap helps it stay on your foot a bit better. All three straps have an adjustable buckle for a great fit. Offered in classic footbed in Habana Oiled Leather. Made in Germany. ', 'Upper material: Oiled Leather - thick yet supple leather is breathable, durable and comfortable. Softens with wear.\r\nFootbed: The classic Birkenstock footbed - features pronounced arch support, a deep heel cup, and a roomy toe box. The footbed conforms to the shape of your foot.\r\n    Sole material: EVA - flexible, lightweight, durable and shock absorbing.\r\n', 'MilanoHabanaOiledLeather.jpg', 'F', 'F'),
(69, 'ACME', 'Triple Straps Sandals', '"Black", "Brown"', 29.9, 'M', 'Casual', 'Sandals', 'Ready to be cool and free with this pair of sandals from ZALORA. Featuring minimal design with buckle details, these trendy sandals are sure to complement your everyday ensemble.', 'Synthetic upper\r\n- Open toecap\r\n- Synthetic suede leather insole with brand detail\r\n- Synthetic outsole', 'TripleStapsSandals.jpg', 'F', 'F'),
(70, 'Nike', 'Nike Romaleos 2', '"White/Black", "Flouroscent Yellow"', 189, 'M', 'Sports', 'Training', 'The Nike Romaleos 2 Men''s Weightlifting Shoe delivers maximum support and a locked-in fit in the gym with integrated lacing, two large midfoot bands and a honeycomb midsole. An innovative thermoplastic heel wedge replaces the wooden version that has been in weightlifting shoes since the 1960s.', 'Synthetic upper for durability and support\r\nIntergrated lacing and two large hook-and-loop midfoot bands for a locked-in feel\r\nElastic on the top of the inside of the shoe flexes with your foot tendons during the snapping "triple extension" movement of the clean and jerk\r\nHoneycomb-like system of trusses and bridges in the midsole for maximum stability\r\nContoured, thermoplastic heel wedge ensures the optimal receiving position and provides maximum support without compression\r\nTwo different sockliners give you versatility for training (softer) and competition (firmer)', 'NikeRomaleos2.jpg', 'F', 'T'),
(71, 'Nike', 'Nike Free Train Versatility', '"Black/Total Orange/Volt"', 90, 'M', 'Sports', 'Training', 'The Nike Free Train Versatility Men''s Training Shoe gives you the flexible support you need for intense and varied workouts. A warp knit upper with Flywire cables offers powerful lockdown, while a revolutionary Nike Free outsole expands and contracts with your foot on every landing.', 'No-sew overlays add lightweight support and durability\r\nHeel loop for easy on and off\r\nDurable Phylon midsole doubles as an outsole for lightweight comfort\r\nMolded sockliner mimics the curvature of the foot for added support\r\nRubber reinforcements enhance durability in key areas\r\nRounded, anatomical heel helps you move naturally', 'NikeFreeTrainVersatility.jpg', 'F', 'F'),
(72, 'Nike ', ' Nike Train Quick Mens', '"Black/Pink/Yellow"', 139.99, 'M', 'Sports', 'Training', 'Make your quickness a weapon during your workouts with these responsive, innovative training shoes.', '\r\n    Molded upper features Flywire tech for a lightweight and innovative lockdown.\r\n    Low-profile IU Foam midsole with recessed PebaxÂ® plate in the forefoot propels your foot forward.\r\n    Rubber outsole lets you accelerate and decelerate on a dime.\r\n', 'NikeTrainQuickMens.jpg', 'T', 'F'),
